snippet.title: You Up with Nikki Glaser
snippet.description: You Up w/ Nikki Glaser channels the energy of a comedy talk show into a podcast. Host Nikki Glaser chats with fellow comedians and interesting people about any topic that gets them going, from oversharing about their personal lives to offering their perspective on sex and dating to making fun of anyone who deserves it.
